Will you please talk to me
for a little bit?

271
00:25:53,533 --> 00:25:54,533
Just for a moment.

272
00:25:56,934 --> 00:25:58,233
You can do that for me, right?

273
00:26:08,834 --> 00:26:10,533
I know that your sister abandoned you.

274
00:26:13,767 --> 00:26:14,767
But...

275
00:26:17,066 --> 00:26:19,100
That train that she left you behind on...

276
00:26:20,800 --> 00:26:23,000
Ever since that train left until now...

277
00:26:25,100 --> 00:26:26,266
she's been waiting for you.

278
00:26:28,667 --> 00:26:30,400
She's been waiting for you...

279
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:34,333
every single second since then.

280
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:42,734
I know that you want
to go back to your sister, too.

281
00:26:44,233 --> 00:26:45,533
You're just afraid

282
00:26:46,934 --> 00:26:48,900
that you'll be abandoned again
if you go back.

283
00:26:50,667 --> 00:26:55,500
Go see her and ask her.

284
00:26:57,633 --> 00:27:01,567
Please meet her and hear her out...

285
00:27:03,767 --> 00:27:04,934
about how she really feels.

286
00:27:45,233 --> 00:27:49,367
<i>Get to Youngshin Station
and come out of Exit Two.</i>

287
00:27:53,600 --> 00:27:55,000
PHARMACY

288
00:27:55,066 --> 00:27:56,433
<i>Go past the pharmacy...</i>

289
00:28:00,266 --> 00:28:01,967
