293
00:28:20,533 --> 00:28:22,000
CHICKEN AND BEER

294
00:28:22,066 --> 00:28:23,934
<i>The chicken place. Cock-a-doodle-doo.</i>

295
00:28:24,667 --> 00:28:25,567
<i>You got that?</i>

296
00:28:32,500 --> 00:28:34,367
<i>No.</i>

297
00:28:34,433 --> 00:28:38,133
